{"tid":2165841,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"俄羅斯反對派領袖納瓦尼疑遭落毒　失去意識送院","createTime":"2020-08-20T05:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T16:31:57.000Z","uid":14918,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c569dc5da41cf2be88121f72d608e2f2dd710c38","tid":2165841,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:23:30.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯反對派領袖納瓦尼（Alexei Navalny）發言人周三（19日）晚表示，納瓦尼疑遭落毒，現時失去意識，在深切治療部接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n發言人亞米什（Kira Yarmish）在Twitter表示，納瓦尼周三早上由托木斯克返回莫斯科期間，在機上感到不適，出現中毒迹象，其後飛機在鄂木斯克緊急落降後立即送院。亞米什懷疑納瓦尼早上飲用的茶混雜毒素，並引述醫生指由於是熱茶，毒素很快被吸收，納瓦尼現時仍未恢復意識。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦尼為俄羅斯著名異見分子，擁有烏克蘭及俄羅斯血統。他於1988年取得法學學位，及後成為律師及活躍於金融界，至2000年正式投身政壇。他在2008年起不時透過網誌，披露俄羅斯政商界的貪腐內幕而聲名大噪，其後多次遭政府針對。納瓦尼去年在拘留期間曾被落毒，亞米什認為他有可能再遭毒手。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53844958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-53844958&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=59e50096\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-53844958&h=843d4168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53844958</a>"},{"pid":"2ca51d6d22aad0806127eed120c11e2d45797236","tid":2165841,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6fbc082a255885714446c552b7729a026968ca","tid":2165841,"uid":61589,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uqF6LG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uqF6LG.jpg&h=a6b2e854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前KGB大佬: <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bfb444a1061c7639f4d0ce222ab90e98654360","tid":2165841,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"仲敢係俄羅斯住"},{